Boolean SnpCreateUIAddMethod::run (  ) 

Functional part of this snippet.

Create a window, and a container panel to frame its components. Add the components to the panel, including a nested container that groups radiobuttons. Add behavior for the OK and Cancel buttons, then display the window.

Returns:
True if the snippet ran as expected, false otherwise
